# 🧠 Employee Attrition Dashboard

An interactive dashboard built using **Streamlit** to analyze and visualize employee attrition patterns. Designed as a strategic insight tool for HR Directors and business stakeholders.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

employee-attrition-dashboard/
│
├── app.py # Main Streamlit application
├── EA.csv # Dataset containing employee attributes and attrition status
├── requirements.txt # List of required Python libraries
└── README.md # Project overview and instructions

yaml
Copy
Edit

---

## 📌 Features

- 📊 20+ interactive visualizations using Plotly, Seaborn, and Matplotlib
- 🎛️ Filters (age, department), sliders, dropdowns, tabs
- 📋 Explanation before each chart (2–3 lines)
- 📈 Heatmaps, bar charts, boxplots, scatter plots, and more
- ✅ A one-stop insight hub for HR strategy and workforce analysis

---

